params.borrowAmount: The amount of tokens to borrow.

returns._0: selectors An array of function selectors.

shift().details: This function adjusts the liquidity positions and distributes staking rewards.It also pays rewards to the caller.

slide().details: This function adjusts the liquidity positions without distributing staking rewards.

addCollateral(uint256).notice: Allows a user to add collateral to their loan.

borrow(uint256,uint256).notice: Allows a user to borrow tokens from the vault's floor liquidity.

defaultLoans().notice: Allows anybody to default expired loans.

getFunctionSelectors().notice: Retrieves the function selectors for this contract.

payback(uint256).notice: Allows a user to pay back a loan.

roll(uint256).notice: Allows a user to roll over a loan.

shift().notice: Shifts the liquidity positions in the vault.

slide().notice: Slides the liquidity positions in the vault.
